title: Team Direct Looking for mid laner
body: Hi guys and gals, we are looking for a mid main that is gold 5+, Discord is a must, headset is a must as well as availability and a friendly personality. Please join the discord channel and ask for catley. Thank you.

replies.body: i'm a mid lane, I think my skill level is around g5 but my rank is s5. Can you give my 1 game to prove myself?
Also I forgot to mention that I can only play around 4 pm to 10 pm.
